dcterms:description: ICIP20 is composed of 6 reference PCs from which 90 degraded versions were derived through three types of compression: V-PCC, G-PCC with triangle soup coding and G-PCC with octree coding.
dcterms:title: ICIP20

dcterms:description: PointXR is composed of 5 PCs from which 45 degraded versions were derived through G-PCC with octree coding for geometry compression and, Lifting and RAHT for color compression.
dcterms:title: PointXR
